<section id="signup">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
        <h3 class="title text-center">Service Provider Sign Up</h3>
        <p>Are you a Service Provider in the Vancouver DTES offering one or more services in any of the following categories: Shelter, Food, Medical, Hygiene, Technology, or Advocacy? If so, you're on the right page!</p>
        <p>Creating a LinkVan account allows you to update the content on your organization's page in the web app. In addition, we provide you basic analytics data for your account.</p>
        <p>Activating an account is easy and absolutely free!</p>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
        	<li><b>Step 1:</b> Fill out the form below to set your password and click Create User.</li>

        	<li><b>Step 2:</b> Tell us if you'd like to create a new listing for your organization OR become the administrator of your organization's page if it's already in the web app.</li>

        	<li><b>Step 3:</b> A member of our team will get in touch with you over the phone as soon as we can to verify your account and help with the initial set up.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          And that's it! Should you have any questions, please reach out to us at <%= mail_to("info@linkvan.ca", "info@linkvan.ca") %>.
        </p>
        <%= render 'form' %>
        <hr>
        <blockquote>
          <p>Teamwork is the ability to work together toward a common vision. The ability to direct individual accomplishments toward organizational objectives. It is the fuel that allows common people to attain uncommon results.</p>
          <footer>Andrew Carnegie</footer>
        </blockquote>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
